casebody.data:
UNITED STATES ARMY CORP OF ENGINEERS, petitioner,
v.
HAWKES CO., INC., et al. No. 15-290. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 11, 2015.

Motion of National Association of Home Builders for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit granted.
